                        <div class="post-heading">
                            <h1>Nutrigenomics: An intro to this newly emerging field</h1> 
                            <h2 class="subheading"></h2> 
                            <span class="meta">
                                Posted by 
                                <a href="">Saanika Agarwal</a> 
                                on August 20, 2022
                            </span>
                            <span class="meta">
                                Edited by 
